column3: “My favorite new strain made into beautiful blonde transparent Honeycomb”
“Great I had a honeycomb extract.  it was almost like sugar cookie doe. the strain was a strong mind high gave me energy but once it wore off I was more tired than usually after smoking something.”
“I love the pink and purple coloring that this bud has. I find the high to be very focused, and energetic.Perfect for getting things done.”
